    question: 'How long does it take to learn how to tread water?',
    answer: 'If you already know the basics of swimming (such as breaststroke or freestyle), learning to tread water comfortably typically takes only 2 to 4 sessions. For absolute beginners, treading water is integrated into our comprehensive 10-12 session course and introduced in the final phases.'
